+<!DOCTYPE html>
+<html lang="en">
+<head>
+  <meta charset="UTF-8">
+  <title>Tenzir Installation</title>
+  <style>
+    body {
+      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
+      font-size: 12px;
+      line-height: 1.5;
+      color: #1d1d1f;
+    }
+    h1 {
+      font-size: 16px;
+      font-weight: 600;
+      margin-bottom: 12px;
+    }
+    h2 {
+      font-size: 14px;
+      font-weight: 600;
+      margin-top: 16px;
+      margin-bottom: 8px;
+    }
+    p, li {
+      margin-bottom: 8px;
+    }
+    code {
+      font-family: "SF Mono", Menlo, Monaco, monospace;
+      font-size: 11px;
+    }
+    a {
+      color: #0b63ce;
+      text-decoration: underline;
+    }
+  </style>
+</head>
+<body>
+  <h1>Tenzir Installation</h1>
+  <p>
+    This package installs Tenzir to <code>/opt/tenzir</code>.
+  </p>
+
+  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
+  <p>After installation, you can:</p>
+  <ul>
+    <li>Run pipelines with the <code>tenzir</code> command</li>
+    <li>Start a node with <code>tenzir-node</code></li>
+  </ul>
+
+  <h2>Documentation</h2>
+  <p>
+    Visit <a href="https://docs.tenzir.com">docs.tenzir.com</a> for
+    comprehensive documentation, tutorials, and guides.
+  </p>
+
+  <h2>Support</h2>
+  <p>
+    For support, visit our <a href="https://discord.tenzir.com">Discord</a>
+    community or contact us at
+    <a href="mailto:support@tenzir.com">support@tenzir.com</a>.
+  </p>
+</body>
+</html>

